text: Ilchigulovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Ilchigulovsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 569 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 49 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Ilchigulovo
